User
    - email (unique)
    - username
    - password
    - role (choices: Admin, Supplier, Customer, Delivery)



PRODUCT
    - supplier (FK to Supplier)
    - product_name
    - product_description
    - product_price
    - product_image
    - stock_quantity
    - category
        + household appliances
        + electronics
        + clothing
        + accessories
        + study materials
        + sports equipment

SUPPLIER
    - user (FK to User)
    - name
    - phone
    - address
Customer
    - user (FK to User)
    - name
    - phone
    - address


SELL
    -PRODUCT (fk)
    -CUSTOMER (fk)

DeliveryPersonnel
- id (PK)
- user (FK to User)
- name
- phone
- address

Order
    - customer (FK to Customer)
    - order_date
    - status (choices: Pending, Processing, Shipped, Delivered, Cancelled)
    - total_amount
    - payment_status (choices: Pending, Paid, Failed)

OrderItem
    - id (PK)
    - order (FK to Order)
    - product (FK to Product)
    - quantity
    - price

Delivery
    - order (FK to Order)
    - delivery_personnel (FK to DeliveryPersonnel)
    - delivery_status (choices: Assigned, In Transit, Delivered)
    - assigned_date
    - delivered_date

Notification
    - user (FK to User)
    - message
    - is_read
    - created_at
